{"tid":1641404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得自己搵唔到人傾訴嘅 或者覺得好攰嘅 入嚟一下","createTime":"2019-10-09T10:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T10:26:16.000Z","uid":312675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"49c26e3892d6a1d544292d9d9cf2ce42719b68e6","tid":1641404,"uid":312675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:26:16.000Z","msg":"我平時都有去發夢，有時會做和理非，但總係覺得好攰，太多野做，做極都做唔停，又好少同人訴苦，所以我得閒會聽下呢幾首歌，聽完之後每次出去都變得更落力更清楚我哋嘅目標，呢幾首歌真係好多聽，每次都聽到起雞皮，同時希望大家有咩想講都可以係到講，等我哋一齊分擔下。珍惜連登，這個家。<br />\n最後同大家分享下啲歌，講清楚先，啲歌版權唔屬於我，只作分享，但我知創作人都係想俾香港人聽，所以我Credit番每首歌嘅制作團隊。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ugsGBd9wmOA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FugsGBd9wmOA&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=78ff6c46\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ugsGBd9wmOA</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7cvcgSKKa5k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7cvcgSKKa5k&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=e4ff7ae0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7cvcgSKKa5k</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RGmWlU2EPF4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRGmWlU2EPF4&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=5ece3d9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RGmWlU2EPF4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2UltvQ1nkuM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2UltvQ1nkuM&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=303c0f0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2UltvQ1nkuM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/imjZ7aHZRuY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FimjZ7aHZRuY&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=b9de5544\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/imjZ7aHZRuY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W7AZdzXXJQc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FW7AZdzXXJQc&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=5a4f2a94\" target=\